    "filename": "rubric.structured.txt",
    "content": "BAREM CHAM DIEM CASE STUDY AREA MANAGER\n\nTong diem toi da: 100\n\nNGUYEN TAC CHAM CHUNG\n- Cham diem theo tung muc ben duoi, khong cong diem cho y khong lien quan.\n- Uu tien bai lam co su dung du lieu, so lieu, bang chung cu the tu dataset/de bai.\n- Neu ung vien co lap luan hop ly, co data chung minh nhung khac dap an mau, van co the cho diem mot phan hoac toi da neu logic vung.\n- Chap nhan sai so ±2% o phan tinh KPI neu phuong phap tinh hop ly.\n- Khong cho diem vuot muc toi da cua moi muc.\n- Khi cho diem tung muc, can neu bang chung cu the tu bai lam.\n\nPHAN 1. PHAN TICH HIEN TRANG - 30 DIEM\n\n1.1. Tinh toan va danh gia KPI - 12 diem\n\n1.1.A. Tinh toan chinh xac - 6 diem\n- Muc 1: Tinh dung KPI trung binh Buu cuc A - toi da 2 diem\n  Dieu kien dat:\n  - GTC tong xap xi 80-81%\n  - GTC TTS xap xi 84-85%\n  - FD xap xi 1.0-1.1%\n- Muc 2: Tinh dung KPI trung binh Buu cuc B - toi da 2 diem\n  Dieu kien dat:\n  - GTC tong xap xi 51-52%\n  - GTC TTS xap xi 53-54%\n  - FD xap xi 1.9-2.1%\n- Muc 3: Tinh dung KPI trung binh Khu vuc - toi da 2 diem\n  Dieu kien dat:\n  - Co tinh trung binh co trong so hoac tong hop hop ly\n\n1.1.B. So sanh va danh gia voi muc tieu - 6 diem\n- Muc 1: So sanh tung KPI voi muc tieu - 2 diem\n  Dieu kien dat:\n  - Co bang hoac noi dung so sanh ro rang tung chi so voi target\n- Muc 2: Xac dinh dung KPI dat/khong dat - 2 diem\n  Dieu kien dat:\n  - Buu cuc A: dat GTC tong, dat GTC TTS, dat FD\n  - Buu cuc B: khong dat ca 3 KPI\n- Muc 3: Danh gia muc do chenh lech - 2 diem\n  Dieu kien dat:\n  - Co neu cu the gap, vi du B thap hon target khoang 28-30% GTC\n\n1.2. Xac dinh van de va nguyen nhan goc re - 12 diem\n\n1.2.A. Xac dinh van de chinh - 4 diem\n- Van de 1: % Gan don Buu cuc B thap, xap xi 74% so voi 99% cua A - 1 diem\n  Ghi chu: insight quan trong nhat\n- Van de 2: % GTC Buu cuc B thap, thap hon A khoang 30% - 1 diem\n- Van de 3: Leadtime Buu cuc B cao, gap khoang 2 lan A - 1 diem\n- Van de 4: Nhan su Buu cuc B bat on, co 4 NV co y dinh nghi - 1 diem\n\n1.2.B. Phan tich nguyen nhan goc re co su dung data - 4 diem\n- Muc 1: Chi ra moi lien he % Gan thap -> GTC thap - 1 diem\n  Dieu kien dat:\n  - Co dan chung so lieu cu the\n- Muc 2: Chi ra moi lien he thieu nhan su -> khong xu ly het don - 1 diem\n  Dieu kien dat:\n  - Co tinh nang luc xu ly so voi don can giao\n- Muc 3: Phat hien pattern theo ngay, Chu Nhat va dau tuan thap hon - 1 diem\n  Dieu kien dat:\n  - Co so sanh data theo thu\n- Muc 4: Phat hien van de thu nhap thap -> NV muon nghi - 1 diem\n  Dieu kien dat:\n  - Co lien he thu nhap trung binh voi ghi chu nghi viec\n\n1.2.C. Logic giai thich - 4 diem\n- Chuoi logic nhan qua ro rang - toi da 2 diem\n  Vi du:\n  - Thieu NV -> Khong gan het don -> Ton don -> Leadtime tang -> FD tang\n- Co so do hoac mo ta moi quan he giua cac yeu to - toi da 2 diem\n  Dieu kien dat:\n  - The hien duoc tu duy he thong\n\nHuong dan cham muc 1.2.C:\n- 4 diem: chuoi logic hoan chinh, co diagram/mo ta ro rang\n- 2-3 diem: co logic nhung chua day du hoac thieu dan chung\n- 0-1 diem: logic roi rac, khong thay moi lien he\n\n1.3. Xac dinh buu cuc uu tien - 6 diem\n- Ket luan dung: Buu cuc B can uu tien - 2 diem\n- Ly do dua tren data van hanh - 2 diem\n  Dieu kien dat:\n  - Dan chung KPI gap, % gan, leadtime\n- Ly do dua tren data nhan su - 2 diem\n  Dieu kien dat:\n  - Dan chung ty le NV muon nghi, nang suat\n\nLuu y phan 1.3:\n- Neu ung vien chon Buu cuc A nhung lap luan hop ly va co data chung minh, van co the cho diem phan lap luan toi da 4/6.\n\nPHAN 2. RA QUYET DINH VA XU LY VAN DE - 50 DIEM\n\n2.1. Chon van de uu tien - 15 diem\n\n2.1.A. Xac dinh van de uu tien - 5 diem\n- Xuat sac - 5 diem\n  Dieu kien dat:\n  - Chon van de cot loi: Nhan su B hoac % Gan B\n  - Day la nguyen nhan goc\n- Tot - 3 den 4 diem\n  Dieu kien dat:\n  - Chon van de quan trong nhung la he qua, vi du GTC thap hoac Leadtime cao\n- Trung binh - 1 den 2 diem\n  Dieu kien dat:\n  - Chon van de dung nhung khong phai uu tien cao nhat\n- Yeu - 0 diem\n  Dieu kien dat:\n  - Chon sai hoac khong chon duoc\n\nDanh sach dap an uu tien cao:\n- On dinh nhan su Buu cuc B, bao gom giu chan 4 NV co y dinh nghi va tuyen bo sung\n- Tang % Gan don Buu cuc B\n- Tang nang luc xu ly don Buu cuc B\n\n2.1.B. Giai thich ly do uu tien theo data - 10 diem\n- Dan chung data cu the - 4 diem\n  Vi du:\n  - 4/20 NV = 20% muon nghi\n- Giai thich tac dong domino - 3 diem\n  Dieu kien dat:\n  - Neu khong giai quyet thi hau qua gi, co logic\n- So sanh voi cac van de khac - 3 diem\n  Dieu kien dat:\n  - Neu ro vi sao van de nay quan trong hon cac van de con lai\n\n2.2. De xuat 3 hanh dong cu the - 35 diem\n\n2.2.A. Hanh dong 1 - 12 diem\n- Muc tieu ro rang - 3 diem\n- Can cu du lieu - 4 diem\n- Ket qua ky vong hop ly - 3 diem\n- Kha thi voi vai tro Area Manager - 2 diem\n\n2.2.B. Hanh dong 2 - 12 diem\n- Muc tieu ro rang - 3 diem\n- Can cu du lieu - 4 diem\n- Ket qua ky vong hop ly - 3 diem\n- Kha thi voi vai tro Area Manager - 2 diem\n\n2.2.C. Hanh dong 3 - 11 diem\n- Muc tieu ro rang - 3 diem\n- Can cu du lieu - 3 diem\n- Ket qua ky vong hop ly - 3 diem\n- Kha thi voi vai tro Area Manager - 2 diem\n\nHuong dan cham cho moi hanh dong:\n- Muc tieu ro rang:\n  - Muc tieu phai cu the, do luong duoc\n- Can cu du lieu:\n  - Phai dan chung data cu the lam co so quyet dinh\n- Ket qua ky vong hop ly:\n  - Realistic, co the dat trong tuan dau hoac giai doan ngan\n- Kha thi voi vai tro Area Manager:\n  - Nam trong quyen han va nguon luc thuc te\n\nHanh dong mau duoc danh gia cao:\n- Gap rieng 4 NV co y dinh nghi de tim hieu va dua giai phap giu chan\n  Ly do tot:\n  - Giai quyet nguyen nhan goc, data-driven\n- Dieu phoi NV tu Buu cuc A sang ho tro B vao ngay cao diem\n  Ly do tot:\n  - Kha thi, dua tren data nang luc xu ly\n- Ra soat va toi uu route/tuyen giao de tang % Gan\n  Ly do tot:\n  - Giai quyet truc tiep van de % Gan thap\n- Dao tao kem cap NV moi cua B, nhom co 5 NV duoi 3 thang\n  Ly do tot:\n  - Data-driven, tang nang suat\n- De xuat tuyen bo sung 2-3 NV cho Buu cuc B\n  Ly do tot:\n  - Giai quyet thieu hut nang luc\n\nHanh dong bi tru diem:\n- \"Hop dong vien nhan vien\" ma khong co plan cu the\n  Ly do tru:\n  - Chung chung, khong data-driven\n- \"Tang cuong giam sat\" ma khong neu giam sat gi\n  Ly do tru:\n  - Khong ro rang\n- Hanh dong nam ngoai quyen han Area Manager\n  Ly do tru:\n  - Khong kha thi\n- Hanh dong khong lien quan den van de da xac dinh\n  Ly do tru:\n  - Khong logic\n\nPHAN 3. LAP KE HOACH CAI THIEN - 20 DIEM\n\n3.1. Muc tieu tung tuan - 8 diem\n- Co muc tieu so cu the cho tung tuan - 4 diem\n  Vi du:\n  - Tuan 1: % Gan dat 80%\n  - Tuan 2: dat 85%\n- Muc tieu co tinh ke thua, tang dan hop ly - 2 diem\n  Dieu kien dat:\n  - Khong nhay vot phi thuc te\n- Muc tieu bam sat KPI yeu cau - 2 diem\n  Dieu kien dat:\n  - Huong den target GTC 80%, FD 1.3%\n\nHuong dan cham muc 3.1:\n- 7-8 diem: day du 4 tuan, moi tuan co 2-3 muc tieu so cu the\n- 4-6 diem: co muc tieu nhung chua du cu the hoac thieu tuan\n- 1-3 diem: muc tieu chung chung, kho do luong\n- 0 diem: khong co muc tieu hoac muc tieu phi thuc te\n\n3.2. Cac hanh dong chinh - 8 diem\n- Hanh dong cu the, chi tiet cho tung tuan - 3 diem\n  Dieu kien dat:\n  - Ai lam, lam gi, khi nao\n- Hanh dong lien ket voi muc tieu tuong ung - 2 diem\n- Hanh dong kha thi voi nguon luc hien co - 2 diem\n  Dieu kien dat:\n  - Dua tren so NV, dac thu Buu cuc\n- Hanh dong co tinh sang tao hoac phu hop thuc te GHN - 1 diem\n\n3.3. Cach theo doi va danh gia - 4 diem\n- Co chi so do luong ro rang - 2 diem\n  Vi du:\n  - % GTC hang ngay, % Gan, so don ton\n- Co tan suat va cach thuc theo doi - 1 diem\n  Vi du:\n  - Review daily/weekly, dashboard\n- Co co che dieu chinh neu khong dat - 1 diem\n  Vi du:\n  - Co plan B neu muc tieu khong dat\n\nBANG TONG HOP DIEM\n- Phan 1. Phan tich hien trang - 30 diem\n  - 1.1. Tinh toan va danh gia KPI - 12 diem\n  - 1.2. Xac dinh van de va nguyen nhan goc re - 12 diem\n  - 1.3. Xac dinh buu cuc uu tien - 6 diem\n- Phan 2. Ra quyet dinh va xu ly van de - 50 diem\n  - 2.1. Chon van de uu tien va giai thich - 15 diem\n  - 2.2. De xuat 3 hanh dong cu the - 35 diem\n- Phan 3. Lap ke hoach cai thien - 20 diem\n  - 3.1. Muc tieu tung tuan - 8 diem\n  - 3.2. Cac hanh dong chinh - 8 diem\n  - 3.3. Cach theo doi va danh gia - 4 diem\n\nTONG CONG: 100 diem",
